    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/a00f0a120fa04901d83de4ccaab81127.poster.avif?t=1765598429\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/a00f0a120fa04901d83de4ccaab81127.webm?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/a00f0a120fa04901d83de4ccaab81127.mp4?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the Attrax technological institute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Opposites attract and likes repel. Enter the mysterious world of Attrax in this captivating single-player demo. Bend the principles of attraction and repulsion to complete 13 puzzle rooms, with each room solved bringing you closer to uncovering the mysteries of the institute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/31b5745bff375445af690c900db5f9bd.poster.avif?t=1765598429\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/31b5745bff375445af690c900db5f9bd.webm?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/31b5745bff375445af690c900db5f9bd.mp4?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attraction and Repulsion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each puzzle room will test your knowledge of attraction and repulsion. Manipulate charged field generators, charged particles, charged cubes, and other activators in different testing environments in order to solve these puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/94214a11de55431243c5f15d1e69dff2.poster.avif?t=1765598429\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/94214a11de55431243c5f15d1e69dff2.webm?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/94214a11de55431243c5f15d1e69dff2.mp4?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Charge Gun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the power of attraction and repulsion into your hands. Use the Charge Gun to directly affect the world around you, flinging objects (yourself included) across rooms to solve intricate puzzles and cross deadly gaps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/3f0b3aba473cab1ed12dc2ce96478aec.poster.avif?t=1765598429\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/3f0b3aba473cab1ed12dc2ce96478aec.webm?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276780/extras/3f0b3aba473cab1ed12dc2ce96478aec.mp4?t=1765598429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the mysteries of the institute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The institute is much older than it wants you to think, and why is it you can't remember how you came to this place. Keep your eyes and ears open as you progress through the Attrax technological institute, or else you might miss the secrets it holds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature List</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 puzzles to solve, a small taste of what the full experience of Attrax has in store for you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A secret room, for those paying close attention</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully re-mappable controls</p></li></ul>",
